{"type": "article", "id": 21610, "title": "FRIENDS OF FRIENDS by Co Partnership", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-01T01:00:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153734uDKOANHhzvFc9Stk.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这瓶高端葡萄酒包装来自澳大利亚平面设计公司 Co Partnership。酒瓶的外形是传统的，但在白色的标签上画出了彩色的卡通图案，像插图一样诙谐有趣。背后的黑色标签纸上是一组三原图的结构，每一个圆圈代表 friend，三个圆的结合点则是酒的名称 FRIENDS OF FRIENDS，也是一种有意思的表现方式。插图设计来自艺术家 Gary Taxali ，这瓶酒的包装设计结合了传统和现代。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153731UnDeljMJCpkqFXSg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153731TWu8FbtB1aJA9xSp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153732Y6dGzjK0MbBR2WDO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061537323KMSOmf7u0VCrzon.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153733HQ2Po1nTGvtCEfRr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}